      right: ["Status epilepticus from abrupt AED withdrawal","Stevens-Johnson syndrome or toxic epidermal necrolysis (widespread rash, mucosal involvement, fever)","Phenytoin toxicity triad: nystagmus → ataxia → altered mental status","Valproate-induced hepatotoxicity (jaundice, coagulopathy, encephalopathy)","Aplastic anemia or agranulocytosis from carbamazepine"]
