      pearl: "Ziprasidone requires administration with food (at least 500 calories) for adequate oral absorption—bioavailability doubles with food; despite its QTc risk, it is metabolically neutral making it paradoxically a good choice for patients with metabolic syndrome IF cardiac risk factors are absent; always obtain baseline ECG"
